9 (a) Matters of mutual concern between state agencies and
10 minority groups;
11 (b) Opportunities to collaborate and increase the accessibility
12 and inclusivity of services delivered to minority groups;
13 (c) The need for state agencies to eliminate systemic racism and
14 structures of racial discrimination within the State of Nevada; and
15 (d) Strategies for ensuring that members of minority groups are
16 able to access programs and services offered by the state agency and
17 interact with the State Government.
18 2. On or before January 1 of each year, the Office of Minority
