21 Governor and to the Director of the Legislative Counsel Bureau for
22 transmittal to the Legislative Commission a report on the findings
23 and recommendations from the [meeting] meetings required by
24 subsection 1.
25 Sec. 2. The provisions of subsection 1 of NRS 218D.380 do
26 not apply to any provision of this act which adds or revises a
27 requirement to submit a report to the Legislature.
28 Sec. 3. This act becomes effective on July 1, 2025.
